You use the hair dryer, you leave the computer on.
你用吹风机，让电脑开着。

175
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:31,760
Do you see what I'm getting at here?
你明白我的意思吗？

176
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:33,880
First phrase, do you see what I'm getting at?
第一个短语，“你明白我的意思吗？”

