That means I haven't said exactly what I mean, but you should understand what I'm saying.
这意味着我没有直接说出我的意思，但你应该理解我在说什么。

180
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:47,480
So he's saying, you're wasting electricity.
所以他在说，“你在浪费电。”

